title: 2010.08.01-F1.12.Hungary.Race.BBC1_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.08.01-F1.12.Hungary.Race.BBC1_UK-TDMK1.m4v

Jake Humphrey presents coverage of the 12th round of the season from the Hungaroring near Budapest, where Lewis Hamilton took the chequered flag last year (Start-time 1.00pm). Hamilton took advantage of front-row starters Fernando Alonso and Sebastien Vettel failing to finish the race, and currently leads the standings by 14 points from team-mate Jenson Button. Alonso was the main talking point at last weekend's German Grand Prix, as he and Ferrari colleague Felipe Massa secured a controversial one-two. Commentary by Jonathan Legard and Martin Brundle.

Now encoded as 'MP4 All Play'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I've made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefully you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3, iPad all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
